<h1>Functions & Tools</h1>
<p>Define callable tools for models that support function/tool calling.</p>
<h2>Definition</h2>
<pre><code>const tools = [{
  name: 'get_weather',
  description: 'Current weather',
  parameters: {
    type: 'object',
    properties: { city: { type: 'string' } },
    required: ['city']
  }
}];
</code></pre>
<h2>Execution Flow</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Model emits tool_call start.</li>
  <li>Stream yields arguments delta.</li>
  <li>Tool resolved, result appended as tool message.</li>
  <li>Model continues / final answer.</li>
</ol>
<p>Multiple tools can be proposed in parallel; the runtime executes sequentially today (parallel planned).</p>
